1954;;Father Brown;;British;;Robert Hamer;;Alec Guinness, Joan Greenwood, Peter Finch;;detective/drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Father_Brown_(film);;Father Brown tries to transport an historically important cross to Rome engaging in battles of wits and faith with a thief and pursuing policeman. The thief, named Flambeau (Finch), is a master of disguise and is elusive, as Father Brown pursues him and tries to convince him to abandon his criminal career.